==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Entrepreneur
<hw>En`tre*pre*neur"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F. See
<er>Enterprise</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Polit. Econ.)</fld> <def>One who takes
the initiative to create a product or establish a business for profit;
generally, whoever undertakes on his own account an enterprise in which
others are employed and risks are taken.</def> <rj><au>F. A.
Walker.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>entrepreneurial</ent>⟦br⟧
